data.description: Discover comfort and convenience at 1787 Forrestdale Dr. This charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home boasts a prime location in a tranquil, well-established neighborhood within walking distance of schools, parks, shopping centers, and Ft. Campbell Military Base. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms upstairs, a bonus room and half bathroom downstairs, the home offers a functional layout. The laundry room offers additional storage options, ensuring functionality meets style. This home provided a turnkey opportunity for a new chapter for the new year. Recent updates include wall and trim paint, new ceiling fans, a new garage door, exterior paint, a gas hot water tank, and a roof replacement in 2017. Also, enjoy the added benefit of no HOA making this residence a truly exceptional find. Seller will provide 6 months home warranty and $2k allowance.
